sub_title: Analyst Corporate Finance at Bit Flow Security Solutions
summary:
Bits Flow is an information technology company with a proven track record in the design, development, implementation, and support of IT Security Solutions for government, multinationals and the private sector in The Netherlands. We offer our customers a complete Security Solutions that strengthen the security posture of their digital infrastructure. This is due to our strong technical competencies in THE FUNDAMENTALS: Networks, Systems, and Applications.

The solutions include:
SECURITY: Cyber (including operational) | Network | System |  Application |  Privacy & Data Protection.
NETWORK engineering.
SYSTEM engineering.
APPLICATION delivery

THESE SERVICES WILL BE AVAILABLE SOON IN SIERRA LEONE & LIBERIA!
